caption:
Our hearts are heavy as the fires in LA continue to grow and containment remains limited, our thoughts are with everyone dealing with the devastation.
 
We will be turning our headquarters into a donation site Tuesday, Jan 14th from 10-4pm.
 
ONeill Headquarters
14350 Myford Rd
Irvine, CA 92606
 
Items were collecting; Blankets, Feminine Items, Baby diapers, Wet Wipes, Drinking Water, First Aid Supplies, Dog/Cat food & more!
 
Please visit our stories for further info and more ways to get involved this weekend or from afar.
 
Stay safe Southern California family.
 
#TeamONeill
